-------Answers-------

i. 

	the function modify sorts the array (flavor of selection sort)

ii.

	at the end of the program some cleanup code been function exit() been called which perform some cleanup code
	finally, the function _exit_halt been called which enters an infiniti loop (flag 1,nop,nop,nop)

iii.

	1.
	replace	: from 0x00010104 to 0x00010120 - 28 bytes
	modify 	: from 0x00010120 to 0x00010180 - 96 bytes
	main	: from 0x00010180 to 0x0001018e - 14 bytes

	2.
	the total size of .text section is 3512 bytes

	3.
	the difference is due to startup code and cleanup code the compiler adds before our main() starts and after
	our main() adds. in addition, there are some padding areas when allignment is needed.

iv.

	out - r7
	in  - r4
